                                    <note>Upper left corner, in pencil by a modern hand: <quote>Brocm. No 5 fol</quote>. Upper right corner, in brown ink by a modern hand (probably <persName ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/person/100536">Nils Reinhold Brocman</persName>): <quote>1480.</quote> Middle of page, left margin, in brown ink by a contemporary hand: <quote>li.vi.</quote> Bottom of page, left margin, in brown ink by a contemporary hand: <quote>baptismi</quote>
